webscript.description:
   This webscript retrieves a page of data on invalid domains. The response will be of the form:
   <pre>
{
   "data":
   {
      "total": 690,
      "pageSize": 5,
      "startIndex": 0,
      "itemCount": 5,
      "items":
      [
         {
            "domain": "antispam.test",
            "type": "ANTISPAM",
            "notes": "a note"
         },
         {
            "domain": "blacklisted.test",
            "type": "BLACKLISTED",
            "notes": "This was blacklisted at request of dfdfdf@sfsds.com"
         }
         // etc...
      ]
   }
}
   </pre>
